platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: You dont need to know a lick of music theory to crank out seriously impressive tunes with Medly. This impressive sequencer lets you create deeply customisable songs with simple gestures: draw a line to add notes, tap to delete, pinch to see the whole track, and more. A variety of instruments help transform each sound, while modifiable mixers and effects ensure limitless ways to fine-tune your creations.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Compose awesome tunes using simple gestures.
